description:
The data shown in Fig. 2a-c in the manuscript is contained in figure2.zip. The raw measured spectra, measurement times, and calibrated Raman shifts for each dose are also included. &nbsp; 
 The unprocessed image data for Fig. 3a-b is contained in figure3.zip. Rows correspond to 1-micron steps. Columns correspond to 7.3 nm steps (100 micron/s stage velocity, 13.73 kSa/s sampling). Measurements used for noise calibration are also included. 
 The unprocessed image data for Fig. 4 is contained in figure4.zip. Rows correspond to 1-micron steps. Columns correspond to 7.3 nm steps (100 micron/s stage velocity, 13.73 kSa/s sampling). Measurements used for noise calibration are also included. &nbsp; 
 Column headers contain additional information.&nbsp;

